plot: Focuses around Thomas and his coming to terms with life and love in England.

During Thomas's club night, a girl named Sophia, high on drugs, jumps from the roof to her death. Thomas suspects that Cook dealt her drugs and picks a fight with him though it's Thomas who faces expulsion from college for his part in Sophia's death. He becomes reckless and aggressive and cheats on his girlfriend Pandora. When Naomi admits that she sold Sophia the drugs, he asks Pandora to take him back, but on Effy's advice she refuses.—don @ minifie-1
